{
  "text": "I was thinking the best way to do the book is to continue working on the history of evolution and its mechanism until we completely make it through the third density and what will occur to the first part of the fourth density, so that the mechanisms of developing the mind, body, spirit complex will be brought out. If I get stymied someplace in one of these sessions as to what questions to ask, in order not to waste time, I may ask some questions that I will use later in the book. But we'll try to always continue along these lines. First question, to go back just a little bit, is what happened to the second density entities who were on this planet, who were unharvestable? I assume there were some that didn't make the harvest into the third density. Can you tell me this? I am raw.",
